    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document updates RFC 5440 to clarify usage of the Local Protection Desired bit signaled in the Path Computation Element Communication Protocol (PCEP).  This document also introduces a new flag for signaling protection enforcement in PCEP.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
